text: Quan Xiang fish porridge at the Bukit Timah interim market. The woman assisting at the stall displayed a very poor attitude, losing her temper over the smallest issues, with her unpleasant behavior witnessed by everyone in the queue. It left a very distasteful experience, and I will not be returning.
The fish soup is served simple, light yet flavorsome. With a delightful amount of fresh and springy fish slices with zero fishy aftertaste.
Quan Xiang at the Bukit Timah interim hawker centre. It is a scam. 9 bucks for this little fish. Attitude from the stall owners or helpers are bad too.
